---
import ConvertedCount from '@/components/react/ConvertedCount';
---

<section class="border-t border-border py-12 sm:py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground">
      Under the hood
    </p>
    <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
      <ConvertedCount client:load /> AMP links converted since 2019
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
      The original AmputatorBot was a Python bot held together with PRAW
      and good intentions. As of 2026 it's rewritten in <strong
        class="text-foreground">Rust</strong> — both for the performance
      improvement and, frankly, because Rust is fun. It's now also a{' '}
      <strong class="text-foreground">Devvit</strong> app for Reddit's new
      Developer Platform, with the legacy Python bot still running in
      parallel as a safety net during the transition.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted-foreground">
      Hosted in the EU on Scaleway (Paris/AMS), open source on GitHub, and
      free to use — same as it's been since day one. The API is public,
      has no auth, and accepts the same query shape it did in 2019, so any
      tool you've wired up against it keeps working.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/KilledMufasa/AmputatorBot"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="font-medium text-brand underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
      >
        View the source →
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/12422626/UVC3n93T"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="font-medium text-brand underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
      >
        Read the API docs →
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.reddit.com/r/AmputatorBot/comments/ch9fxp/changelog_of_amputatorbot/"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="font-medium text-brand underline-offset-4 hover:underline"
      >
        Changelog →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
